Two simple html pages with Javascript interacions:

1. myGhosts.html
This page will contain the drawing of pacman's ghost in SVG and with canvas. 
Interactions within the page are in the description of the html(They are provided when html is openned).

2. myPolygon.html
This page will contain the drawing of a polygon in canvas. 
Interactions with the polygon are in the descrpition of the html also.

3. display.js
Javascript to create canvas drawing and update the interface based on the interactions made by the user for both SVG and canvas.

4. polygon.js
Javascript to create canvas and update the interdace based on the interactions made by the user. 
